title: *PATREON PREVIEW* AMA After Dark 2: The Return Pt. II
description: The Core Four quite drunkenly return to the hot seat, answering your questions in the finale of our latest AMA. Topics include, but are not limited to: corporate spending, in person podcasting, 180 degree style shifts, big and tall sizing, cardigans, newsletters, grail daydreaming, Asian hate crimes, professional obligations, relocation, blunt wraps, ALD, BAPE, fruit, cancel culture, cooking, body counts, resort footwear, first big fashion purchases and much more.
